# NRI KAONA Design System

Derived from the NRI Journal (野村総合研究所) editorial aesthetic and the shadcn/ui component library, tailored for a desktop-first Japanese HR information system.

---

## Brand Context

**Product**: 人材情報システム (Human Resource Information System)
**User**: HR staff / managers on desktop browsers (1280–1440px viewport)
**Tone**: Professional, editorial, precise — inspired by NRI's clean corporate identity

---

## Color Palette

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|-------|-----|-------|
| `--nk-blue` | `#1A52A6` | Primary brand, active nav, selected tab indicator, primary buttons |
| `--nk-blue-light` | `#EBF1FB` | Active tab/row background, info badge fill |
| `--nk-blue-dark` | `#143D80` | Hover state for primary blue |
| `--nk-black` | `#111111` | Headings, heavy CTAs, logo |
| `--nk-gray-900` | `#171717` | Primary body text |
| `--nk-gray-700` | `#374151` | Secondary text, nav items |
| `--nk-gray-500` | `#6B7280` | Captions, labels, placeholder |
| `--nk-gray-300` | `#D1D5DB` | Disabled states |
| `--nk-gray-100` | `#F3F4F6` | Page background, active nav pill |
| `--nk-gray-50` | `#F9FAFB` | Card inner backgrounds |
| `--nk-white` | `#FFFFFF` | Card surface, sidebar, top bar |
| `--nk-border` | `#E5E7EB` | All dividers, card borders, input borders |
