## Typography

**Font Stack**: `'Inter', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif`
- Inter for Latin characters (all weights 250–900 available)
- Noto Sans JP for Japanese characters (variable font, 100–900)

| Role | Size | Weight | Color |
|------|------|--------|-------|
| App title | 13px | 700 | `#111111` |
| Section heading (card) | 16px | 700 | `#111111` |
| Subsection / 身上書セクション見出し | 13px | 700 | `#1A52A6` |
| Body / table cell | 13px | 400 | `#171717` |
| Label / field name | 13px | 500 | `#6B7280` |
| Caption / metadata | 11px | 400 | `#9CA3AF` |
| Nav item | 13px | 500 | `#374151` |
| Badge text | 11px | 600 | varies |
| Large stat number | 32px / 40px | 800 | `#111111` |

**Click-through HTML prototype**: `public/nri-kaona/index.html` — left rail switches **基本情報 / 身上書 / スキル / キャリア / 自己申告** (vanilla JS in `app.js`). Deployed at `/nri-kaona` on Vercel.

