## Layout

### Page Shell (Desktop, 1280px)

```
┌────────────────────────────────────── 1280px ──────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Top App Bar (56px)  [Brand] [Horizontal Nav]                     [Search] [Avatar]│
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── │
│  Profile Rail (220px) │  Main Content (1060px)                                      │
│  - Photo + name/ID    │  [Breadcrumb bar 40px]                                      │
│  - Profile tabs       │  [Scrollable cards]                                         │
└───────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── │
```

### Top App Bar
- Height: 56px, `background: #FFFFFF`, `border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB`
- Left: 4-dot NRI brand icon (2×2 grid, `#1A52A6`) + product name + subtitle
- Center: Horizontal global nav pills (ホーム, 検索, 管理, その他) — active uses `#F3F4F6` fill
- Right: 検索結果 pill + avatar circle

### Profile Rail
- Width: 220px, Height: 100%, `background: #FFFFFF`, `border-right: 1px solid #E5E7EB`
- Top section (padded): circular avatar placeholder + employee name (700, 15px) + ID + dept
- Tab list (scrollable): all profile sections — active tab uses `background: #EBF1FB`, `border-left: 3px solid #1A52A6`, `color: #111111`; inactive: `color: #6B7280`
- Tabs: 基本情報, 身上書, キャリア, スキル, 採用時情報, 勤怠情報, 自己申告, 人事記録, 審査書類, 転入時面談

### Main Content Area
- `background: #F3F4F6`, padding: 0
- Breadcrumb bar: 40px, `background: #FFFFFF`, `border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB`
- Content padding: 20px

